sentences.sContent: North Korea is a more extreme example of external power being incommensurate with internal stability and wealth.
sentences.sContent_eng: North Korea is a more extreme example of external power being incommensurate with internal stability and wealth.
sentences.sCn: 朝鲜是一个外部力量与内部稳定和财富不相称的更极端例子。

synos.tran: 不适应的；不相称的；不成比例

remMethod.val: in(不) + commensurate(成比例的， 相称的) → 不成比例的， 不相称的

trans.tranCn: 不成比例的， 不相称的
